Rules.InvariantScript:
UpdateContext({visibleIn2:false});
If(
    IsBlank(CbOrg2.SelectedItems),Notify("You must select a sponsor name", NotificationType.Error),
    If(IsBlank(SourceIn.Selected.Value), Notify("You must select a Source of Donation", NotificationType.Error),
    If(IsBlank(ProductTypeIn.Selected.Value), Notify("You must select a Product Type", NotificationType.Error),
    If(Not IsNumeric(QtyIn.Text),Notify("You must enter quantity in number", NotificationType.Error),


Collect(ProductIntake,
{IntakeDate: IntakeDateIn.SelectedDate, 
UWBCRegionID: RegionIn.SelectedText.Value, 
Community:CityIn.SelectedText.Value, 
SponsorNameNew:CbOrg2.Selected.'Organization Name',
Qty:QtyIn.Text, 
ProductType:ProductTypeIn.SelectedText.Value, 
AndarID:AndarIDIn.Text,
DonationTypeNew:SourceIn.SelectedText.Value,
ID: IdIn.Text});
ResetForm(IntakeForm_Input);
Navigate('Intake Form_Input', ScreenTransition.Fade)
    ))))
